---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Privacy Policy" 
  description="Privacy policy for Honda Civic Blog."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-black text-4xl mb-8 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center mb-12">
          Last updated: February 2026
        </p>
        
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          Honda Civic Blog collects minimal information from visitors. We may collect:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Analytics Data</strong> - Anonymous usage statistics including pages visited, 
          referral sources, device type, and approximate location (country/region level)</li>
          <li><strong>Contact Information</strong> - Name and email address when you contact us 
          through our contact form</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>
          We use the information we collect to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Understand how visitors use our site</li>
          <li>Improve our content and user experience</li>
          <li>Respond to inquiries submitted through our contact form</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use cookies to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Remember your dark/light mode preference</li>
          <li>Collect anonymous analytics through Google Analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> - For website analytics</li>
          <li><strong>Cusdis</strong> - For comments (if enabled)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>
          Analytics data is retained according to the default Google Analytics settings. 
          Contact form submissions are retained only as long as necessary to respond to 
          your inquiry.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          You have the right to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Request access to any personal data we hold about you</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your personal data</li>
          <li>Opt out of analytics tracking by using browser extensions or settings</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          Honda Civic Blog does not knowingly collect information from children under 13 
          years of age. If you believe we have inadvertently collected such information, 
          please contact us.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted 
          on this page with an updated revision date.
        </p>
        
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please 
          <a href="/contact/">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
